(51, 'P00051', 'dewalt-dcb127-b1-108v-20ah-xr-li-ion-battery-pack-2', 'Dewalt (DCB127-B1) 10.8V 2.0Ah XR Li-Ion Battery Pack', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt', 3290.00, 1888.00, 'DW010', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Dewalt DCS491NT XJ - 18 V, Metal Shear has an accurate sheet metal cutting solution. It has an easy to handle tool to cut duct work on ground and overhead. Metal Shear has a variable speed trigger and D handle that allows the users to push through a cut 360 degreesâ€™ tool-free swivel head. Dewalt DCS491NT XJ enables users to access tight quarters while maintaining comfort. Users can make precise cutting patterns with the help of electronic speed regulation. Also, it has a high-quality steel blade that assures problem-free continuous operation and maximum service life. DeWalt Metal Shear can perform a double cut to reduce deformation of the work piece.</span>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-04-18 20:19:09', '2023-04-18 20:19:09'),
