(240, 'P00240', 'stanley-scbl01-b1-20v-37mm-brushless-blower-bare-tool', 'STANLEY SCBL01-B1 20V 37mm Brushless Blower (Bare tool)', 'power-tools', NULL, 'stanley-2', 10000.00, 6092.00, 'SCBL01-B1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>Variable speed trigger allows you to adjust the blower speed for controlled clear up and clean down.</li><li>Deflator port allows you to connect the nozzle to turn the blower into a deflator, increasing the versatility of the blower.</li><li>High performance centrifugal fan high performance, high efficiency Increased runtime and blower speed.</li><li>Ergonomic and lightweight design For higher productivity.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'STANLEY SCBL01-B1 20V 37mm Brushless Blower (Bare tool)1683358502.jpg', '2023-05-06 07:35:02', '2023-05-06 07:35:02'),
(241, 'P00241', 'stanley-drill-sdh600-in-rotary-hammer-drill-13-mm-chuck-size-600-w', 'STANLEY DRILL SDH600-IN Rotary Hammer Drill  (13 mm Chuck Size, 600 W)', 'power-tools', NULL, 'stanley-2', 4295.00, 2806.00, 'SDH600-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>STANLEY SDH600 13 mm impact hammer drill helps you by efficiently drilling holes through wood, steel, and masonry. This hammer drill has a smart speed dial that offers multiple preset speed settings for better drilling output and control. With dual-drilling modes, you can use this equipment as a hammer or drill according to your requirement.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'STANLEY DRILL SDH600-IN Rotary Hammer Drill  (13 mm Chuck Size, 600 W)1683358628.webp', '2023-05-06 07:37:08', '2023-05-06 07:37:08'),
(242, 'P00242', 'stanley-sdh600kp-in-diy-13-mm-hammer-drill-machine-and-hand-tool-kit-for-home-use-120-pieces', 'STANLEY SDH600KP-IN DIY 13 mm Hammer Drill Machine and Hand Tool Kit for Home Use (120-Pieces)', 'power-tools', NULL, 'stanley-2', 7600.00, 6208.00, 'SDH600KP-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>The hammer drill kit contains 120 pieces, including hammer drill, drill bits, screw bit holder, hammer, measurement tape, utility knife, universal plier, Lineman tester, Allen key set, interchangeable screw bits, screws &amp; plug set and other tools.</li><li>The lightweight, compact &amp; ergonomic tool design provides a high level of precision, control and consistency to the task at hand and mitigates the risk of injury.</li><li>The hammer drill contained within the kit is powered by a 600 W tool motor with dual modes for drilling &amp; hammering and forward/reverse switch for both clockwise &amp; counter-clockwise rotation.</li><li>The tool kit has several tools for precise measuring, fastening and maintenance applications. It includes hex keys for fastening hex bolts, universal pliers, measuring tapes and precision drill bits.</li><li>600 watts powerful motor for higher tool performance.</li><li>2 Tools in 1: Blower and vacuum cleaner. Cord Length: 3 m.</li><li>Light and compact design for ease of handling, Detachable Nozzle. Used for Industry Cleaning and House Cleaning.</li><li>Optimized fan structure for better airflow ; variable speed option for easy control of airflow.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'STANLEY SDH600KP-IN DIY 13 mm Hammer Drill Machine and Hand Tool Kit for Home Use (120-Pieces)1683358823.jpg', '2023-05-06 07:40:23', '2023-05-06 07:40:23'),
