(268, 'P00268', 'stanley-ss30-in-300w-random-orbital-sander-125mm-5', 'STANLEY – SS30-IN 300W Random Orbital Sander 125mm (5″)', 'power-tools', NULL, 'stanley-2', 6790.00, 4477.00, 'SS30-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>Stanley SS30-IN is a professional finish sander that is ergonomically designed for a comfortable grip and low vibration for use in various sanding applications, especially for wood and wood finishes. It has a velcro pad for easy fixing and removal of sandpaper. The sander has a powerful 300W motor that is durable and efficient. The random orbital motion leaves minimal sanding marks on the sanded surface. The variable speed feature allows for easy control of the sander on various types of surfaces, be it softwood, hardwood, or wood finishes. The rocker switch is insulated to prevent dust from entering the switch. The Sander also has a dust collection system, that is very useful in sanding applications. The dust collection bag can be easily attached and detached to aid in the removal of collected dust.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'STANLEY – SS30-IN 300W Random Orbital Sander 125mm (5″)1683365685.jpg', '2023-05-06 09:34:45', '2023-05-06 09:34:45'),
