(271, 'P00271', 'stanley-sm18-b1-1800w-compound-mitre-saw', 'Stanley SM18-B1 1800W Compound Mitre Saw', 'power-tools', NULL, 'stanley-2', 40000.00, 22128.00, 'SM18-B1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>Stanley SM18-B1 1800W Compound Mitre Saw is a powerful and versatile saw that is perfect for a variety of woodworking and carpentry projects. With a powerful 1800 watt motor, it can easily handle even the most challenging cuts. It has a powerful 1800 watt motor and a no-load speed of 4800 rpm.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Stanley SM18-B1 1800W Compound Mitre Saw1683366318.jpg', '2023-05-06 09:45:18', '2023-05-06 09:45:18'),
