(278, 'P00278', 'blackdecker-bcrt8k35-b1-8v-15ah-cordless-rotary-tool-with-35-piece-accessory-set', 'BLACK+DECKER BCRT8K35-B1 8V 1.5Ah Cordless Rotary Tool With 35-Piece Accessory Set', 'power-tools', NULL, 'black-decker', 6419.00, 3471.00, 'BCRT8K35-B1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>The Black and Decker KR704REK-IN is a powerful and versatile hammer drill designed for both professional and DIY use. It features a 710-watt motor that delivers efficient performance for drilling through various materials such as wood, metal, and masonry.</p><p>This drill has a variable speed feature that lets you adjust the speed of the drill as per the application, providing greater control and accuracy. Additionally, it has a hammer function that makes it suitable for drilling into concrete, brick, and other tough materials.</p><p>The KR704REK-IN has a keyless chuck system that allows you to change bits quickly and easily without the need for any tools. It also has a depth gauge that lets you set the drilling depth for increased precision and accuracy.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'BLACK+DECKER BCRT8K35-B1 8V 1.5Ah Cordless Rotary Tool With 35-Piece Accessory Set1683371480.jpg', '2023-05-06 11:11:20', '2023-05-06 11:11:20'),
