(280, 'P00280', 'blackdecker-hammer-drill-kr704rek-in-impact-driver', 'BLACK+DECKER hammer drill KR704REK-IN Impact Driver', 'power-tools', NULL, 'black-decker', 5004.00, 2933.00, 'KR704REK-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>The KR704REK-IN features a powerful 710 watt motor that delivers high-performance drilling and offers a variable speed control that allows you to adjust the drilling speed based on the material you are working with. It has a maximum drilling capacity of 13mm in concrete, 13mm in steel, and 30mm in wood. The tool is also equipped with a reversible function that allows you to easily switch between forward and reverse modes.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'BLACK+DECKER hammer drill KR704REK-IN Impact Driver1683371707.webp', '2023-05-06 11:15:07', '2023-05-06 11:15:07'),
