(320, 'P00320', 'blackdecker-pi100la-b2c-100w-dc-to-ac-car-power-inverter-for-charging-laptop-in-car', 'BLACK+DECKER PI100LA-B2C 100W DC to AC Car Power Inverter for Charging Laptop in Car', 'power-tools', NULL, 'black-decker', 3857.00, 1365.00, 'PI100LA-B2C', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>Premium 100W car power inverter with a USB port and AC outlet. USB port can charge most phones and tablets while AC outlet is great for charging laptop, breast pump, nebulizer, game console, kindle, TV, DVD players, lights, iPad, and other electronic devices</li><li>A 100W power inverter has a multifunction socket. It has continuous output power rated 100W.</li><li>Rated input and output voltage are 12.8V and 220-240 AVC.</li><li>It has an LED indicator, also gives Overload Protection and short circuit protection.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'BLACK+DECKER PI100LA-B2C 100W DC to AC Car Power Inverter for Charging Laptop in Car1683523725.jpg', '2023-05-08 05:28:45', '2023-05-08 05:28:45'),
(321, 'P00321', 'blackdecker-8-ltr-thermoelectric-portable-automotive-car-beverage-cooler-warmer-bdc8-la', 'Black+Decker 8 ltr Thermoelectric Portable Automotive Car Beverage Cooler & Warmer -BDC8-LA', 'power-tools', NULL, 'black-decker', 9229.00, 7413.00, 'BDC8-LA', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>The Automotive Car Beverage Cooler and Warmer by Black+Decker in an excellent way of keeping your drinks fresh and cool/warm while you are on the go. This dual utility product is highly portable and can be a great companion for you during your road trip. The Black+Decker\'s cooler and warmer is made out of excellent quality plastic material which ensures durability and high work performance for the product.&nbsp;</p><p>The Automotive Car beverage cooler comes packed with a number of exceptional features which makes it a preferred choice for the consumers.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Black+Decker 8 ltr Thermoelectric Portable Automotive Car Beverage Cooler & Warmer -BDC8-LA1683524106.jpg', '2023-05-08 05:35:06', '2023-05-08 05:35:06');
