(357, 'P00357', 'dewalt-dwe493-in-large-angle-grinder-2200-w-180-mm', 'Dewalt DWE493-IN Large Angle Grinder (2200 W, 180 mm)', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 11990.00, 7194.00, 'DWE493-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>Dewalt DWE493-IN Large Angle Grinder (2200 W, 180 mm) is one of a kind. This product is primarily used to grind metal and polish glass. This product is highly efficient and has great speed. Dewalt is a leading brand that manufactures power tools and sells them all over the world. This product leads a little to the heavy side, it weighs about 5.1 Kg, well the density defines the strength of this product.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DWE493-IN Large Angle Grinder (2200 W, 180 mm)1683533178.webp', '2023-05-08 08:06:18', '2023-05-08 08:06:18'),
(358, 'P00358', 'dewalt-dwe497-in-2600w-180mm-heavy-duty-large-angle-grinder-with-des-technology-and-innovative-anti-vibration-system-perform-and-protect-shield', 'DEWALT DWE497-IN 2600W 180mm Heavy Duty Large Angle Grinder with DES Technology and Innovative Anti Vibration System-Perform and Protect Shield', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 13590.00, 8154.00, 'DWE497-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>Anti-vibe trigger handle reduces user fatigue caused by vibration.</li><li>Power-loss reset is a perform and protect control feature that prevents accidental re-starts following a power disruption when the tool is left in the \"on\" position.</li><li>Dust ejection System increases brush life.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'DEWALT DWE497-IN 2600W 180mm Heavy Duty Large Angle Grinder with DES Technology and Innovative Anti Vibration System-Perform and Protect Shield1683536055.jpg', '2023-05-08 08:54:15', '2023-05-08 08:54:15'),
(359, 'P00359', 'dewalt-d28413-in-2200w-180mm-heavy-duty-large-angle-grinder-black-yellow', 'DEWALT D28413-IN 2200W 180mm Heavy Duty Large Angle Grinder (Black & Yellow)', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 15590.00, 9354.00, 'D28413-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>It has a 2200 W, 8500 RPM Machine.</li><li>Soft start to limit start-up current &amp; reduce kick back.</li><li>Anti vibration side handle.</li><li>Quick adjustment tool free guard.</li><li>Abrasion protected high power motor for increased motor durability. Five position side handleCut-off brushes to prolong motor life. New Switch with Lock-on.</li><li>Five position side handle for improved balance in cutting and grinding applications.</li><li>Cut-off brushes to prolong motor life.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'DEWALT D28413-IN 2200W 180mm Heavy Duty Large Angle Grinder (Black & Yellow)1683536208.jpg', '2023-05-08 08:56:48', '2023-05-08 08:56:48'),
(360, 'P00360', 'dewalt-dwe4597-in-7-inch-49-hp-angle-grinder', 'Dewalt DWE4597-IN 7 inch, 4.9 HP Angle Grinder', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 25990.00, 15594.00, 'DWE4597-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>Dewalt DWE4597 is a powerful angle grinder used for numerous purposes. This 7-inch angle grinder is ideal for grinding metal and for polishing stone or granite. It can also be used for metal cuttings. This 4.9 HP angle grinder is equipped with an E-Clutch system which shuts off the system as soon it detects a wheel punch. The dust removal system guarantees the longevity of the motor and brushes. This angle grinder comes with a soft grip handle to make it easy to hold while you work. Dewalt DWE4597 - 4.9 HP, 7 inch Angle Grinder is one of the best angle grinders which comes with anti-vibration triggers to assure stress-free operation. It is a portable grinder which can be carried anywhere you want.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DWE4597-IN 7 inch, 4.9 HP Angle Grinder1683536391.jpg', '2023-05-08 08:59:51', '2023-05-08 08:59:51'),
(361, 'P00361', 'dewalt-d25733k-qs-8-kg-1600-w-sds-max-hammer-with-anti-rotation', 'Dewalt D25733K-QS - 8 Kg, 1600 W SDS Max Hammer with Anti Rotation', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 74390.00, 52073.00, 'D25733K-QS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>The red indicator LED illuminates when the E-Clutch System is engaged.</li><li>Tool maintains speed under heavy loads, including in higher PSI concrete, allowing the user to get the job done faster.</li><li>Gives users the ability to drill and demolish concrete in one tool, saving them money by not needing to buy and maintain 2 tools.</li><li>Service brush light near the handle notifies the user when it\'s time to take the tool in for service.</li><li>Protects users from the effects of vibration, including numbness and tingling in the hands, allowing them to get work done more quickly without fatigue.</li><li>Offers users more control by adjusting speed of drilling or chipping based upon the thickness and density of the material they are working with.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt D25733K-QS - 8 Kg, 1600 W SDS Max Hammer with Anti Rotation1683537894.png', '2023-05-08 09:24:54', '2023-05-08 09:24:54'),
(362, 'P00362', 'dewalt-d25773k-qs-10-kg-1700-w-sds-max-hammer-with-anti-rotation', 'Dewalt D25773K-QS - 10 Kg, 1700 W SDS Max hammer with Anti Rotation', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 76690.00, 53683.00, 'D25773K-QS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>Active vibration control system incorporating a counter balance mass and floating handle delivers extremely low vibration.</li><li>An anti rotation system detects a loss of tool control and reacts by instantly cutting the power.</li><li>2 stage clutch system that allows the user to change the clutch level from low to high torque to optimize the tool for specific drilling applications.</li><li>Electronic speed and impact energy control.</li><li>Lock on switch for chipping.</li><li>Rotation stop for demolition applications in brick; masonry and light chasing in concrete.</li><li>Brush wear and service indicators.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt D25773K-QS - 10 Kg, 1700 W SDS Max hammer with Anti Rotation1683538045.png', '2023-05-08 09:27:25', '2023-05-08 09:27:25'),
(363, 'P00363', 'dewalt-d25899k-qs-10kg-sds-max-demolition-hammer-19j-impact-energy', 'DEWALT D25899K-QS 10KG SDS-Max Demolition Hammer-19J Impact Energy', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 56090.00, 39263.00, 'D25899K-QS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>The Dewalt D25899K-QS 10kg 1500W SDS-Max Demolition Hammer is the perfect tool for demolishing concrete, masonry, and other hard surfaces. With its high power and durable construction, this hammer will quickly and easily break down walls, floors, and other structures. The Dewalt D25899K-QS is an amazing demolition hammer that comes with a 10kg Tool Holder and an uncertainty of 1.5 Sq m/s. This hammer is perfect for those that need an impact hammer with a large impact energy. This hammer is also ideal for small demolition jobs as it has a power input of 1500 W.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'DEWALT D25899K-QS 10KG SDS-Max Demolition Hammer-19J Impact Energy1683538213.jpg', '2023-05-08 09:30:13', '2023-05-08 09:30:13'),
(364, 'P00364', 'dewalt-d21585-qs-2500w-250mm-3-speed-wet-drill-machine-motor', 'DEWALT D21585-QS 2500W 250mm 3 Speed Wet Drill Machine Motor', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 167000.00, 116900.00, 'D21585-QS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>Ideal tool for heavy duty electrical, plumbing, HVAC or general construction applications when drilling into concrete.</li><li>To be used with D215851 drilling stand Integrated water swivel for core drilling into any material up to 250 mm.</li><li>3 Mechanical speeds deliver optimum drilling speed Overload and thermal protection for life of the tool.</li><li>Mechanical clutch for added user protection.</li><li>Integrated water swivel for core drilling into any material up to 250 mm.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'DEWALT D21585-QS 2500W 250mm 3 Speed Wet Drill Machine Motor1683538359.jpg', '2023-05-08 09:32:39', '2023-05-08 09:32:39'),
(365, 'P00365', 'dewalt-26-nm-versa-clutch-screwdriver', 'Dewalt 26 Nm Versa Clutch Screwdriver', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 24190.00, 16933.00, 'DW268-B1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>All Dewalt 26 Nm Versa Clutch Screwdriver, DW268-B1 are manufactured by using quality assured material and advanced techniques, which make them up to the standard in this highly challenging field. The materials utilized to manufacture Dewalt 26Nm Versa Clutch Screwdriver, DW268-B1, are sourced from the most reliable and official vendors, chosen after performing detailed market surveys. Dewalt products are widely acknowledged in the market for their high quality.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt 26 Nm Versa Clutch Screwdriver1683538529.jpg', '2023-05-08 09:35:29', '2023-05-08 09:35:29'),
(366, 'P00366', 'dewalt-dw269-b1-540w-screw-driver-0-1000-rpm', 'Dewalt DW269-B1 540W Screw driver (0-1000 RPM)', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 26990.00, 18893.00, 'DW269-B1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>Helical-cut steel, heat-treated steel gears for long life and durability.</li><li>High power motor for metal fastening applications.</li><li>Versa-Clutch torque adjustment system \"dials in\" the proper torque needed to efficiently drive fasteners without stripping or breaking fasteners.</li><li>Rubber grip and two-finger trigger for increased comfort and greater control.</li><li>Metal nose and gear case for durability on the job.</li><li>Excellent ergonomics offers less user fatigue.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DW269-B1 540W Screw driver (0-1000 RPM)1683538669.jpg', '2023-05-08 09:37:49', '2023-05-08 09:37:49'),
