(380, 'P00380', 'dewalt-dch333x2-qw-xr-flexvolt-sds-hammer-drill-54v-0-1000-rpm', 'Dewalt DCH333X2-QW XR Flexvolt SDS+ Hammer Drill 54V 0-1000 RPM', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 94890.00, 66423.00, 'DCH333X2-QW', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>The DCH333X2 is part of the 54v Flexvolt range which provides cordless power tools with the equivalent power output as corded power tools. The DeWalt Hammer Drill will provide unrivaled performance on the job site thanks to the Brushless 9.0Ah 18v Li-Ion Battery Platform which supplies extreme runtime performance and reduced maintenance. The DCH333X2 has 3 primary modes of operation including Hammer, Rotary only and Chisel only, making this an extremely versatile tool which is ideal for drilling anchors and fixing holes into concrete, brick and masonry from 4mm to 30mm.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DCH333X2-QW XR Flexvolt SDS+ Hammer Drill 54V 0-1000 RPM1683542546.webp', '2023-05-08 10:42:26', '2023-05-08 10:42:26'),
(381, 'P00381', 'dewalt-dcs388t2-qw-reciprocating-saw', 'Dewalt DCS388T2-QW Reciprocating Saw', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 68390.00, 47873.00, 'DCS388T2-QW', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>The DCS388T2-QW reciprocating saw is a powerful saw with plenty of features. With 54 V and 6 Ah, this saw has the power to cut through pretty much anything. The dual position blade clamp allows for flush cutting and increased versatility. The tool free blade change allows for quick blade changes without the use of any tools which makes it a great time saving tool. With a no load stroke rate of 2400 spm, this saw can make quick work of any task. This reciprocating saw comes with two batteries, a charger and carrying case.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DCS388T2-QW Reciprocating Saw1683542663.webp', '2023-05-08 10:44:23', '2023-05-08 10:44:23'),
