(400, 'P00400', 'dewalt-dcf620nt-xj-18-v-xr-drywall-screw-driver-tstak-without-battery', 'Dewalt DCF620NT-XJ - 18 V XR Drywall Screw Driver Tstak Without Battery', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 19390.00, 13573.00, 'DCF620NT-XJ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>Dewalt DCF620NT-XJ - 18 V XR Drywall Screw Driver Bare Tstak is made up of efficient fitting of drywall. Drywall Screw Driver is comfortable to work with this device even in a small space area. There is a comfortable collated screw magazine for quick cleaning of drywall dust. There is a trick lock to work without trigger activation. Dewalt DCF620NT XJ has a job site robust gearing to withstand the harshest of conditions. It has a convenient adjustable rotating belt hook suitable for both left and right-handed users to fix the tool onto the belt.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DCF620NT-XJ - 18 V XR Drywall Screw Driver Tstak Without Battery1683547556.png', '2023-05-08 12:05:56', '2023-05-08 12:05:56'),
(401, 'P00401', 'dewalt-vacuum-cleaner-54v-black-dcv586mn-xj', 'Dewalt Vacuum Cleaner 54V Black DCV586MN-XJ', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 46962.00, 32873.00, 'DCV586MN-XJ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>Includes a remote for wireless operation.</li><li>Audible alarm alerts user of a drop in performance.</li><li>Automatic filter cleaning every 30 seconds, reduces filter clogging delivering constant air flow.</li><li>Wet and Dry pick up with variable suction control allows for the reduction of suction power if required.</li><li>M Classified to meet EU legislation.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt Vacuum Cleaner 54V Black DCV586MN-XJ1683547699.webp', '2023-05-08 12:08:19', '2023-05-08 12:08:19'),
(402, 'P00402', 'dewalt-dcb127-xj-20-ah-108-v-xr-li-ion-battery-pack', 'Dewalt DCB127-XJ - 2.0 Ah, 10.8 V XR Li Ion Battery Pack', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 3290.00, 2303.00, 'DCB127-XJ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>Dewalt DCB127-XJ - 2.0 Ah, 10.8 V XR Li-Ion Battery Pack comes in lightweight design providing the user to use the device with ease. XR Li-Ion Battery has no memory effect and no self-discharge for increasing productivity and less downtime. Dewalt DCB127-XJ is compatible with all DeWalt 10.8 v tool with slide pack design. It has an absorber for the acidity of batteries.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DCB127-XJ - 2.0 Ah, 10.8 V XR Li Ion Battery Pack1683547880.png', '2023-05-08 12:11:20', '2023-05-08 12:11:20'),
(403, 'P00403', 'dewalt-d215851-xj-stand-for-drilling-motor', 'Dewalt D215851-XJ - Stand for Drilling Motor', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 127200.00, 89040.00, 'D215851-XJ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>The Dewalt D215851-XJ Drilling Stand is a drilling motor stand manufactured by Dewalt which is a brand widely known for producing power tools for construction industries. The stand is used to secure a drilling motor in place so that it can be used in heavy-duty drilling in concrete.</p><p>The Heavy-duty Drill Stand has a large base which provides high stability and accuracy. It also has transport wheels so as to provide easy access to the user at the construction site. The smooth sliding mechanism of the carriage makes for good drilling accuracy. It is easy to use as it has an integrated vacuum base, which makes the set up quicker. The support brackets make the column rigidity higher.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt D215851-XJ - Stand for Drilling Motor1683548045.png', '2023-05-08 12:14:05', '2023-05-08 12:14:05'),
(404, 'P00404', 'dewalt-d25301d-xj-dust-extractor-telescope-with-hose-for-sds-rotary-hammer', 'Dewalt D25301D-XJ - Dust Extractor Telescope with Hose for SDS Rotary Hammer', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 10390.00, 7273.00, 'D25301D-XJ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>Dewalt D25301D-XJ - Dust Extractor Telescope with Hose for SDS Rotary Hammer filters dust and debris during heavy drilling tasks. Dust extraction system runs for the next 2 seconds after the machine is turned off to perform efficient cleaning. SDS Rotary Hammer comes with an integrated depth stop. Up to 5/8” diameter carbide drill bits can be used. Dewalt D25301D XJ weighs only 2.6 lbs. Due to its compact size, it can be used even in congested spaces and have more visibility. Replaceable dust nozzle is included in the system. There is a quick fit system for easy tool-free attachment and release. The user gets a dust extractor telescope with a side handle and hose.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt D25301D-XJ - Dust Extractor Telescope with Hose for SDS Rotary Hammer1683548354.png', '2023-05-08 12:19:14', '2023-05-08 12:19:14'),
(405, 'P00405', 'dewalt-d25304dh-xj-integrated-hammer-drill-dust-extractor', 'Dewalt D25304DH-XJ - Integrated Hammer Drill Dust Extractor', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 19790.00, 13853.00, 'D25304DH-XJ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>Dewalt D25304DH-XJ - Integrated Hammer Drill Dust Extractor can perform dust-free drilling up to 26 mm in diameter. There is a high-quality HEPA filter that is capable of maintaining efficiency even with the small dust particles. Integrated Hammer Drill Dust Extractor can also do deep drilling up to 180 mm while maintaining a clean environment. Dewalt D25304DH-XJ has a quick one-handed release hammer that requires no additional accessories to operate it. It is extremely tough and versatile enough to do all types of applications. DeWalt Hammer Drill has extra comfort and balance due to compact design and low weight.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt D25304DH-XJ - Integrated Hammer Drill Dust Extractor1683548518.png', '2023-05-08 12:21:58', '2023-05-08 12:21:58'),
(406, 'P00406', 'dewalt-dwe492-in-large-angle-grinder-2200-w-230-mm', 'Dewalt DWE492-IN Large Angle Grinder (2200 W, 230 mm)', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 13390.00, 9373.00, 'DWE492-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>Longer service life of carbon brush.</li><li>Dust proof construction.</li><li>Wattage : 2200 Watt.</li><li>Increased service life of carbon brush.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DWE492-IN Large Angle Grinder (2200 W, 230 mm)1683551069.webp', '2023-05-08 13:04:30', '2023-05-08 13:04:30'),
(407, 'P00407', 'dewalt-dwe496-in-large-angle-grinder-2600-w-230-mm', 'Dewalt DWE496-IN Large Angle Grinder (2600 W, 230 mm)', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 14190.00, 9933.00, 'DWE496-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>Dewalt DWE496-IN 230 mm, 2600 W Large Angle Grinder comes with an air vent for better tool cooling optimization. It has popped off the brush to avoid abrasion. Large Angle Grinder has a lock on switch with ergonomic design and three-position side handle. It is majorly used in the construction site. It has a dust ejection system to extend the life of the device. There is overload protection that prevents the tool from overheating and limit start-up current. Dewalt DWE496 has an anti-vibration side handle that allows the user to perform fatigue-free performance. It has a quick tool-free guard brush window that allows user to replace the brush easily. The spindle lock is added for quick wheel change option. Usually, it comes with inner and outer disc flanges and spanner.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DWE496-IN Large Angle Grinder (2600 W, 230 mm)1683551269.webp', '2023-05-08 13:07:49', '2023-05-08 13:07:49'),
(408, 'P00408', 'dewalt-dwe4579-qs-230-mm-wheel-dia-6500-rpm-large-angle-grinder', 'Dewalt DWE4579-QS 230 mm Wheel Dia 6500 RPM Large Angle Grinder', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 29990.00, 20993.00, 'DWE4579-QS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>Anti-Vibration side handle reduces the users exposure to vibration, a Perform &amp; Protect Vibration Feature.</li><li>Heavy Duty Large Angle Grinder, Wheel Dia 180mm, No load Rpm 8500, Power Input Watt 2700.</li><li>Power-Off Advanced Electronic Overload Protection shuts the tool off before it reaches overload or burn-up.</li><li>Low profile gearcase allow for work in tight areas.</li><li>Automatic turn-off brushes shut down the tool when brushes need to be changed to avoid tool damage.</li><li>Anti-Vibe Trigger Handle reduces user fatigue caused by vibration.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DWE4579-QS 230 mm Wheel Dia 6500 RPM Large Angle Grinder1683608933.webp', '2023-05-09 05:08:53', '2023-05-09 05:08:53'),
(409, 'P00409', 'dewalt-dwe4887n-in-heavy-duty-die-grinder-450-w-38-mm', 'Dewalt DWE4887N-IN Heavy Duty Die Grinder (450 W, 38 mm)', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 10200.00, 7140.00, 'DWE4887N-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>450W, 25,000 rpm motor provides high power and speed for all 38mm grinding applications.</li><li>Convenient paddle switch for easy gripping.</li><li>Lock-off switch prevents accidental start-up.</li><li>Precision 6mm collet securely holds all proper accessories.</li><li>Paddle switch with no lock.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DWE4887N-IN Heavy Duty Die Grinder (450 W, 38 mm)1683609306.jpg', '2023-05-09 05:15:06', '2023-05-09 05:15:06'),
(410, 'P00410', 'dewalt-die-grinder-with-slider-lock-450w-6mm', 'DEWALT DIE GRINDER WITH SLIDER LOCK 450W 6MM', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 11800.00, 8260.00, 'DWE4884-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>Long nose with rubber grip improves access, comfort and control.</li><li>Anti-lock collet ensures that all attachments are easily removable once the nut is loosened.</li><li>Powerful 450W motor allows maximum performance in demanding applications.</li><li>Ergonomic, lock-on-slide switch for maximum flexibility.</li><li>Cut-off brushes to prolong motor life.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'DEWALT DIE GRINDER WITH SLIDER LOCK 450W 6MM1683609433.webp', '2023-05-09 05:17:13', '2023-05-09 05:17:13'),
(411, 'P00411', 'dewalt-dwe4997-qs-1300w-6mm-brushless-variable-speed-die-grinder', 'DEWALT DWE4997-QS 1300W 6mm Brushless Variable Speed Die Grinder', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 29690.00, 20783.00, 'DWE4997-QS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>Brushless motor for long motor life and no brush changes.</li><li>Precision 1/4\" collet with 1/8\" reducing sleeve for gripping strength and allows user to operate both 1/4\" and 1/8\" shaft accessories.</li><li>AC/DC capacity works off welding machines and generators for productivity and versatility.</li><li>Spindle lock button for quick accessory change.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'DEWALT DWE4997-QS 1300W 6mm Brushless Variable Speed Die Grinder1683610405.jpg', '2023-05-09 05:33:26', '2023-05-09 05:33:26'),
(412, 'P00412', 'dewalt-dw871-in-chop-saw-14-inch', 'Dewalt DW871-IN Chop saw 14 Inch', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 23090.00, 16163.00, 'DW871-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>Dewalt DW871-IN Chop saw 14 Inch. The handle offers superior ergonomics by providing a better grip and more comfortable hand position, reducing fatigue, thereby increasing productivity. Durable metal top provides easy mobility of the saw. Engineered for increasing performance and durability, the powerful 2200 watts electric motor provides overload capacity. Provided with a quick-release fence, quick lock for fast and easy material clamping and 100% ball and roller bearings for smoother operations, this yellow tool has the facility of spindle lock too that allows users to change the wheels quickly and easily along with saving time and money. Smooth movement and greater durability are ensured by heavy-duty compression spring, whereas the heavy-duty lockdown pin helps users to lock the saw head in the carrying position. Easily accessible brushes help in minimizing the downtime by allowing for convenient servicing on the work-site.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DW871-IN Chop saw 14 Inch1683610545.webp', '2023-05-09 05:35:46', '2023-05-09 05:35:46'),
(413, 'P00413', 'dewalt-d28730-in-355-mm-2300-w-industrial-chop-saw', 'Dewalt D28730-IN 355 mm, 2300 W Industrial Chop Saw', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 18590.00, 13013.00, 'D28730-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>15.0 Amp/4.0HP maximum motor HP motor provides overload protection, increasing performance and durability.</li><li>Ergonomically designed \"D\" handles provide a more comfortable hand position, reducing fatigue and increasing productivity.</li><li>Quick Lock Vise allows for fast clamping on different size materials to increase productivity.</li><li>45 Degree pivoting fence allows for fast and accurate angle cuts.</li><li>Integrated top handle allows the saw to be carried around easily.</li><li>On board wheel change wrench allows for convenient storage and greatly reduces the risk of lost wrenches.</li><li>High performance aluminium oxide grain wheels provide for long life, fast cutting, and smoother running wheels.</li><li>Compression spring provides smoother movement and increased durability versus torsion springs.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt D28730-IN 355 mm, 2300 W Industrial Chop Saw1683610757.png', '2023-05-09 05:39:17', '2023-05-09 05:39:17'),
(414, 'P00414', 'dewalt-d28870-in-355mm-2200w-heavy-duty-chop-saw', 'Dewalt D28870-IN 355mm 2200W Heavy Duty Chop Saw', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 20690.00, 14483.00, 'D28870-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>Capacity in mm: at 90 degree-- Square: 120, Rectangle: 100 x 120, Right angle: 140, Round: 130.</li><li>Capacity in mm: at 45 degree-- square: 105, rectangle: 100 x 140, right angle: 120, round: 113.</li><li>It has a powerful 2200 watt motor and weighs 18kg with a no load speed of 3800 rpm.</li><li>It gives you accurate cuts for different profiles (round, rectangle and square).</li><li>It can cut the materials at an angle of 45 or 90 degree based on the requirement.</li><li>It has an ergonomic design which supports long duration tool usage.</li><li>It has tool-free wheel changes and is easy to transport.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt D28870-IN 355mm 2200W Heavy Duty Chop Saw1683611017.jpg', '2023-05-09 05:43:37', '2023-05-09 05:43:37'),
(415, 'P00415', 'dewalt-dwe1622k-in-1200w-50mm-2-speed-magnetic-drill-press', 'Dewalt DWE1622K-IN 1200W 50mm 2 Speed Magnetic Drill Press', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 93890.00, 65723.00, 'DWE1622K-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>Delivers high level of performance for fast, clean and accurate drilling into steel.</li><li>Compact and light weight unit.</li><li>Overload protection with 3 stage LED indicator.</li><li>The universal quick release cutter holder : It accepts any annular cutter with 19 mm round shank (Weldon) with one or more flats.</li><li>No volt switch prevents inadvertent restart after power failure.</li><li>Standard Equipment: 3 jaw chuck with adaptor for straight shank drill bits, safety chain, lubrication system, drill guard, kit box.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DWE1622K-IN 1200W 50mm 2 Speed Magnetic Drill Press1683612114.webp', '2023-05-09 06:01:55', '2023-05-09 06:01:55'),
(416, 'P00416', 'dewalt-dwp849x-in-180mm-electronic-sander-polisher', 'Dewalt DWP849X-IN 180mm Electronic Sander & Polisher', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 19490.00, 13643.00, 'DWP849X-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>Dewalt 180mm DWP849X Electronic Sander &amp; Polisher is an innovative and lightweight sanding tool. It provides high power for the job and is available lightweight for painters to make painting surfaces ready. You can get this tool at variable speed and provides a range of 0-600/ 0-3500 rpm and features a vacuum hose to remove potentially harmful dust. It is strongly recommended to use for better results and for the long life of the sander machine.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DWP849X-IN 180mm Electronic Sander & Polisher1683612260.webp', '2023-05-09 06:04:21', '2023-05-09 06:04:21'),
(417, 'P00417', 'dewalt-dw752r-b5-150-mm-373-w-bench-grinder', 'Dewalt DW752R-B5 - 150 mm, 373 W Bench Grinder', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 10890.00, 7623.00, 'DW752R-B5', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>Dewalt DW752R-B5 - 373 W, 150 mm Bench Grinder has a powerful motor engine that provides maximum power and torque for various applications. It has 152 Mm wheel with coarse and medium grain for applications like grinding, smoothing and polishing. DeWalt Bench Grinder has metallic support and precision machinery that allows the user to have good control over the Bench grinder.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DW752R-B5 - 150 mm, 373 W Bench Grinder1683612419.jpg', '2023-05-09 06:06:59', '2023-05-09 06:06:59'),
(418, 'P00418', 'dewalt-dw714-in-254-mm-1650-w-compound-mitre-saw-with-80t-aluminium-blade', 'Dewalt DW714-IN 254 mm, 1650 W Compound Mitre Saw with 80T Aluminium Blade', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 27690.00, 19383.00, 'DW714-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>Dewalt DW714-IN 254mm Compound Mitre Saw with 80T Aluminium Blade comes with 45 degrees pivoting fence that enables the user to do fast and accurate angle cut. It has a steel base to weld jigs or stops directly onto the plate. Dewalt DW714 has a heavy lockdown pin that allows the head of the saw to be locked in a carrying position without using chain. There is a quick lock vise that allows for fast clamping on different size materials. It helps in increasing the productivity, performance and durability of the compound mitre saw.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DW714-IN 254 mm, 1650 W Compound Mitre Saw with 80T Aluminium Blade1683612653.png', '2023-05-09 06:10:53', '2023-05-09 06:10:53'),
(419, 'P00419', 'dewalt-dws715-in-1600w-305mm-single-bevel-mitre-saw', 'DEWALT DWS715-IN 1600W 305mm Single Bevel Mitre Saw', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 50490.00, 35343.00, 'DWS715-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>15 Amp motor, 4000 rpm extended power and durability.Adjustable stainless steel miter detent plate with 11 positive stops improves productivity.Tall sliding fence supports crown molding up to 5-1/4 Inch nested and base molding up to 6-1/2 Inch vertically Lightweight, built-in carrying handle for portability.4 Hardened Steel Bevel Stops at 0, 33.9, 45 and 48 Degree delivers versatility at most common bevel angles.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'DEWALT DWS715-IN 1600W 305mm Single Bevel Mitre Saw1683612882.jpg', '2023-05-09 06:14:42', '2023-05-09 06:14:42'),
(420, 'P00420', 'dewalt-305mm-compound-slide-mitre-saw-with-variable-speed-dws780-qs', 'Dewalt 305mm Compound Slide Mitre Saw with Variable Speed DWS780-QS', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 97690.00, 68383.00, 'DWS780-QS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>Integrated CUTLINE(TM) Blade Positioning System provides adjustment free cut line indication for better accuracy &amp; visibility.</li><li>Exclusive back fence design cuts up to 2x16“ wood at 90° &amp; 2x12” at 45°.</li><li>Compact, lightweight design allows for easy transport &amp; storage.</li><li>Dual horizontal steel rails with innovative clamping mechanism.</li><li>Adjustable stainless steel miter detent plate with 10 positive stops.</li><li>Innovative gearbox and belt-drive design increases vertical cutting capacity.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt 305mm Compound Slide Mitre Saw with Variable Speed DWS780-QS1683613072.jpg', '2023-05-09 06:17:53', '2023-05-09 06:17:53'),
(421, 'P00421', 'dewalt-dwe349-in-20-mm-500-w-pendulum-jig-saw', 'Dewalt DWE349-IN - 20 mm, 500 W Pendulum Jig Saw', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 8790.00, 6153.00, 'DWE349-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>Compact, ergonomic, design gives user comfort and versatility in use.</li><li>A 500 watt motor gives performance and durability.</li><li>Low profile dust extraction shield with bi-directional vacuum spout for clean, efficient cutting performance.</li><li>Quick and easy patented keyless blade change system.</li><li>3-position pendulum action controls the aggressiveness or smoothness of cuts.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DWE349-IN - 20 mm, 500 W Pendulum Jig Saw1683613238.png', '2023-05-09 06:20:39', '2023-05-09 06:20:39');
