(430, 'P00430', 'dewalt-dch333nt-xj-54-v-xr-sds-plus-hammer', 'Dewalt DCH333NT-XJ - 54 V, XR SDS Plus Hammer', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 51790.00, 36253.00, 'DCH333NT-XJ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>Dewalt DCH333NT-XJ - 54 V, XR SDS Plus Hammer Bare offers high runtime and performance ranging from 54 volts to 18 volts. It works on a brushless motor for more power, longer runtime and less maintenance. XR SDS Plus Hammer Bare works on three modes, namely hammer drilling, drilling and chiseling plus anti-vibration technology to deliver fatigue-free performance. Dewalt DCH333NT-XJ has a maximum drill capacity of 30mm in concrete and impacts energy of 3.5 joules. It is suitable for heavy-duty construction applications that can be performed without using mains power. DeWalt SDS Plus Hammer is used for drilling anchors and fixing holes into concrete, brick and masonry from 4mm to 30mm.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DCH333NT-XJ - 54 V, XR SDS Plus Hammer1683616303.jpg', '2023-05-09 07:11:43', '2023-05-09 07:11:43'),
