(432, 'P00432', 'dewalt-dcd700d2-in-108-v-13-ah-10-mm-compact-drill-driver', 'Dewalt DCD700D2-IN 10.8 V 1.3 Ah 10 mm Compact Drill Driver', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 13000.00, 9100.00, 'DCD700D2-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>Dewalt 10.8V, 1.3Ah, 10 mm Compact Drill Driver, DCD700D2-IN</p><p>This premium quality product is made up of high quality materials and is designed for long lasting, heavy duty usage. This tool is ideal for the home and also works well in professional settings where a long lasting router is required. This product comes with a powerful motor that produces more power. It has a corded design which makes it easy to use in any weather conditions. A drill driver is a type of power tool that is used for drilling holes and driving screws. It combines the functions of a drill and a screwdriver into a single tool, making it a versatile tool for many DIY and construction tasks. A drill driver typically has a motor that drives a rotating chuck, which holds the drill bit for the screwdriver bit. The tool is designed to apply torque to the bit, allowing it to bore into wood, metal, plastic, and other materials.&nbsp;</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DCD700D2-IN 10.8 V 1.3 Ah 10 mm Compact Drill Driver1683616728.webp', '2023-05-09 07:18:48', '2023-05-09 07:18:48'),
(433, 'P00433', 'dewalt-dcd710d2-in-108v-max-xr-li-ion-compact-drill-driver', 'Dewalt DCD710D2-IN 10.8V Max XR Li-ion Compact Drill Driver', 'power-tools', NULL, 'dewalt-2', 13500.00, 9450.00, 'DCD710D2-IN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>With a lightweight and compact design, Dewalt DCD710D2-IN Max XR Li-ion Compact Drill Driver comes with a powerful 180 Watt motor with a speed of 1500 rpm and 2 Ah XR Li-ion battery. It comes with 15 positions adjustable torque control that allows consistent screw driving into different materials. The parabolic switch profile provides better control. This compact drill driver comes with a 10 mm single sleeve chuck with automatic spindle lock that helps in the quick and easy change of bits. The 2-speed settings along with electronic motor brakes further improve control and increase efficiency. This drill driver has a high-performance fan that cools the motor and increases durability. It has metal gearing for efficient power transmission and extended lifespan of the tool. The ergonomically designed rubber handle enhances user comfort and reduces fatigue. The LED light in this Dewalt compact drill driver improves visibility and accuracy.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DCD710D2-IN 10.8V Max XR Li-ion Compact Drill Driver1683616884.jpg', '2023-05-09 07:21:24', '2023-05-09 07:21:24'),
