(576, 'P00576', 'dewalt-dch133m1-qw-brushless-sds-plus-hammer-26-mm-18v-3', 'Dewalt DCH133M1-QW Brushless SDS Plus Hammer (26 mm, 18V)', 'power-tools', 'None', 'dewalt-2', 34190.00, 23933.00, 'DCH133M1-QW', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<ul><li>Brushless motor with high capacity XR 4.0ah 18v lithium-ion battery.</li><li>Solid performance and fast drilling speed in all key diameters as corded.</li><li>2.6 joules impact energy provides corded power without the cord.</li><li>Compact, lightweight and ergonomic design for improved comfort and support during extended operating periods.</li><li>Mechanical clutch for user and unit protection.</li><li>Low vibration for prolonged trigger times.</li><li>Brushless Motors provide up to 57% longer life and a longer life of the machine in comparison to conventional engines with carbon brushes.Requires no brush changes and is lighter compared to brushed grinder.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DCH133M1-QW Brushless SDS Plus Hammer (26 mm, 18V)1683795534.jpg', '2023-05-11 08:58:54', '2023-05-11 08:58:54'),
(577, 'P00577', 'dewalt-dcb606-b1-18-by-54-v-flexvolt-battery-60ah', 'Dewalt DCB606-B1 18 by 54 V Flexvolt Battery 6.0Ah', 'power-tools', 'None', 'dewalt-2', 16890.00, 11823.00, 'DCB606-B1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'in_stock', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p>The XR FLEXVOLT battery offers 54V of run-time, power and efficiency in a compact design. This two pack of batteries is compatible with all XR tools that use a traditional 18v Lithium Ion battery but will not work with the Milwaukee M18 Fuel 4 Tool Pack. The state of charge indicator on the battery body lets you know exactly how much run time you have remaining.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Dewalt DCB606-B1 18 by 54 V Flexvolt Battery 6.0Ah1683795800.webp', '2023-05-11 09:03:20', '2023-05-11 09:03:20'),
